10 August 1999
Last night I went skating with a group called Inline Swine. Far as I can tell, they don&rsquo;t associate themselves with the name so much as associating themselves with, &ldquo;we meet on Tuesdays and Thursdays at 8pm at Texas Art Supply.&rdquo;
I found the group while skating alone downtown 3 weeks ago. They were about a block away so I caught up with them. I discovered they were cool and they skate regularly so I may hook up with this group regularly!
